    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="blog-article">
            <div class="block-title"> 

                <h3>Drupal 8 : Moins de &laquo; Drupalisme &raquo; vers plus de standardisation</h3>
                <h5 class="section-description">Mars 2016</h5>
            </div>
            <p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <table>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><span style="color: #000000;"><img src="http://tchida.net/images/blog/image4.png" alt="logo" width="179" height="198" /></span></td>
                        <td>
                            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Afin d'am&eacute;liorer la performance et la viabilit&eacute; d&rsquo;un CMS, un catalyseur est des fois n&eacute;cessaire : dans notre cas c&rsquo;est <strong>Symfony2</strong>.</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">La diff&eacute;rence majeur entre <strong>Drupal 8</strong> et ces pr&eacute;c&eacute;dentes version est l'int&eacute;gration du <strong>Framework Symfony2</strong> et c&rsquo;est au niveau d&eacute;veloppement que l'on trouve les plus grands changements.</span></p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">La sortie de </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal 8</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> a &eacute;t&eacute; illustr&eacute; par l&rsquo;int&eacute;gration des composants de </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Symfony2 </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">et les bonnes pratiques manquantes jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; pr&eacute;sent telles que la programmation orient&eacute;e objet, les tests unitaires, une approche en API ReST et aussi twig comme moteur de template rendant le theming plus accessible.</span></span></p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cette derni&egrave;re version de </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">apporte plusieurs innovations et de grosses &nbsp;plus value &agrave; savoir : </span></span></p>
            <ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L'adoption de l'approche</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> "Mobile First" pour un Front-Office et le Back-Office responsive. </span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L'int&eacute;gration de </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">la version 4 de </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">CKEditor</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">,</span> <span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">ce dernier permet &nbsp;le &ldquo;inline editing&rdquo; ou la possibilit&eacute; d'&eacute;diter un champ sans passer par le formulaire d&rsquo;&eacute;dition complet. </span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L&rsquo;abandon du syst&egrave;me de template &ldquo;PHPTemplate&rdquo; au profit de </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">TWIG </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">qui utilise une syntaxe intuitive et simple ainsi que plein d&rsquo;autre avantages, un pas de plus vers l&rsquo;utilisation des standard du web. </span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #3b3b3b; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Une nouvelle architecture bas&eacute;e sur le Framework Symfony 2 qu&rsquo;on verra plus en d&eacute;tail dans ce qui suit. </span></li>
            </ul>
            <h4 style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 20pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 17pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Focus sur l'architecture </span></h4>
            <h2 style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">La programmation orient&eacute;e objet</span></h2>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Les anciennes versions de </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">se basent sp&eacute;cialement sur la programmation proc&eacute;durale. Cette nouvelle version suit et adopte la notion de programmation orient&eacute;e objet. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Maintenant, on utilise donc des classes, des interfaces, l'h&eacute;ritage, l'injection de d&eacute;pendance, l'autoloading, les annotations PHP... </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://tchida.net/images/blog/image7.png" alt="" width="412" height="162" /></span></span></p>
            <h2 style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Les composants principaux Drupal &amp; Symfony2</span></h2>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal 8</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> requiert, au minimum, &nbsp;la version </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">5.4.5</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> de </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">PHP</span> <span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">(contrairement &agrave; &nbsp;5.2.5 pour son pr&eacute;d&eacute;cesseur). Cette nouvelle version utilise les classes et les interfaces, mais aussi les namespaces et la norme </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">PSR-4</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. Ceci est le signe d&rsquo;une v&eacute;ritable r&eacute;-architecture du CMS, et pour cause, seulement 20% du code originel de Drupal 7 a &eacute;t&eacute; conserv&eacute;.</span></span></p>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cette nouvelle architecture</span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Drupal </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">n&rsquo;&eacute;tend pas le noyau </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Symfony</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, comme le ferait une application web </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Symfony2</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. Elle offre le m&ecirc;me type de fonctionnalit&eacute; mais en impl&eacute;mentant l'interface de ce noyau. Ceci est parce que </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal 8</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> ne partage pas l'approche des &laquo;Bundles&raquo; de </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Symfony</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. Ces &nbsp;Bundles offrent un excellent moyen de cr&eacute;er des applications Web personnalis&eacute;es, mais ils sont moins adapt&eacute;s &agrave; la construction d'un CMS qui doit &ecirc;tre tr&egrave;s flexible et extensible. Le </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">DrupalKernel</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> charge l'environnement (services et modules disponibles) d'une mani&egrave;re l&eacute;g&egrave;rement diff&eacute;rente (mais similaire) que le noyau </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Symfony</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, mais il d&eacute;l&egrave;gue la gestion des Requests/Responses et du routing aux composants HttpKernel &amp; HttpFoundation, tout comme le noyau de </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Symfony</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> fait.</span></span></p>
            <ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">HttpFoundation</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> : D&eacute;finit une couche orient&eacute;e objet pour la sp&eacute;cification HTTP. fournit aussi une abstraction pour les requ&ecirc;tes, les r&eacute;ponses, les t&eacute;l&eacute;chargements de fichiers, les cookies, les sessions...</span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">HttpKernel</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> : Fournit les briques de construction afin de b&acirc;tir des Framework HTTP souples et performants.</span></span></li>
            </ul>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Routing :</span></strong> Permet d&rsquo;associer une requ&ecirc;te HTTP &agrave; un ensemble de variables de configuration pouvant &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;es dans du code en utilisant les fonctions de rappel PHP. Ce qui simplifie la d&eacute;finition d&rsquo;URLS facilement indexables sans avoir recours &agrave; un fichier .htaccess encombr&eacute; et complexe.</span></span></p>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://tchida.net/images/blog/image6.png" alt="" width="347" height="310" /></span></span></p>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">En outre, </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal 8</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> apporte ses propres composants et le code de base. Un aper&ccedil;u sch&eacute;matique est repr&eacute;sent&eacute; dans l'image suivante.</span></span></span></p>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://tchida.net/images/blog/image2.png" alt="" width="617" height="723" /></span></span></span></p>
            <ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Event Dispatcher :</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Permet l&rsquo;impl&eacute;mentation du patron de conception M&eacute;diateur d&rsquo;une mani&egrave;re simple et efficace pour rendre les projets PHP facilement extensibles ceci en rendant la communication plus simple et facile entre les classes. </span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Dependency</span></strong> <strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Injection :</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Standardise et centralise la mani&egrave;re dont les objets sont construits dans une application. Renforce la modularit&eacute; du CMS gr&acirc;ce &agrave; une gestion dynamique des d&eacute;pendances entre classes.</span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Serializer :</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Permet la conversion des objets PHP dans un format sp&eacute;cifique (XML, JSON, YAML...) et inversement.</span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">YAML :</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Analyse des cha&icirc;nes de caract&egrave;res YAML afin de les convertir en tableaux PHP. permet aussi la conversion des tableaux PHP en cha&icirc;nes de caract&egrave;res YAML. </span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Classe Loader :</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Charge les classes du projet automatiquement si elles respectent les conventions standards de PHP.</span></span></li>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Validator :</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Simplifie les callbacks de contrainte, utile pour la validation de donn&eacute;es et am&eacute;liore la validation des images.</span></span></li>
            </ul>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Translation :</span></strong> Incorpor&eacute; &agrave; <strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal 8</span></strong>, ce composant fournit les outils n&eacute;cessaires pour concevoir des syst&egrave;mes de rendu (Templates).permet d&rsquo;&eacute;crire le code de mani&egrave;re &agrave; ce que les classes puissent &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;es et test&eacute;es <em>unitairement</em></span></span></span></p>

            <h2 style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Composant drupal 8 </span></h2>
            <p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 34pt; margin-bottom: 22pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">La particularit&eacute; ainsi que la force de drupal r&eacute;side dans son extensibilit&eacute;. Pour le moment cette nouvelle version int&egrave;gre un nombre limit&eacute; de modules </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">op&eacute;rationnels, </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">2,299</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> contre </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">12,432</span></strong> <span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">pour la version 7. On remarque que quelques modules importants ne sont toujours pas compatible, &agrave; savoir : </span></span></p>

            <ul>
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #202026; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Webform : </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Permettant la gestion des formulaires et l&rsquo;enregistrement ainsi que l&rsquo;export des r&eacute;sultats </span></strong></span></li>
            </ul>

            <ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #202026; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Panels : </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Permettant une gestion simple de la cr&eacute;ation des pages, bien que disponible sous </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal 8</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> sous version beta, ce module reste encore immature et n&rsquo;egale pas son pr&eacute;d&eacute;cesseur en convivialit&eacute;. </span></span></li>
            </ul>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><em><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Views data export : </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Permettant, via une interface graphique, &nbsp;un export des donn&eacute;es, &agrave; partir des View et &nbsp;sous plusieurs formats ( CSV, XLS, DOC, XML&hellip;) </span></em></span></span></span></p>

            <h4 style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 34pt; margin-bottom: 22pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 17pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Ce qui change vraiment pour le d&eacute;veloppeur &nbsp;</span></h4>
            <h2 style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Les customs &nbsp;modules Drupal 8</span></h2>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cette nouvelle version de <strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Drupal </span></strong>impose une nouvelle structure de fichiers pour les modules d&rsquo;extension mais aussi un nouveau standard de d&eacute;veloppement. &nbsp;</span></em></span></span></span></p>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://tchida.net/images/blog/image5.png" alt="" width="302" height="164" /></span></em></span></span></span></p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Le module standard est constituait de : </span></p>
            <p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></em></span></span></span></p>
            <ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Un fichier </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">module.info.yml</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, contenant la d&eacute;claration du module (nom, description, type&hellip;)</span></span></li>
            </ul>
            <p><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://tchida.net/images/blog/image8.png" width="649" height="103" /></span></span></p>
            <ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Un fichier </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">module.routing.yml</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, ce dernier int&eacute;grant les routes sera utilis&eacute; par le composant </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Routing </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">de Symfony2</span></span></li>
            </ul>
            <p><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://tchida.net/images/blog/image3.png" alt="" width="649" height="103" /></span></span></p>
            <ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
                <li style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Ubuntu; color: #434343; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><em style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="vertical-align: baseline;">Un contr&ocirc;leur<strong><span style="vertical-align: baseline;"> ModuleController.php</span></strong>, qui va contenir les d&eacute;claration des fonctions </span></em></span></li>
            </ul>
            <p><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><em style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://tchida.net/images/blog/image1.png" alt="" width="648" height="466" /></span></em></span></p>
            <h2 style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Vue et template en twig </span></h2>
            <p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Le syst&egrave;me </span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">TWIG </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">apporte un plus pour la s&eacute;curit&eacute; en utilisant une syntaxe simple et intuitive ne permettant plus l'ex&eacute;cution de code PHP. Les templates sont moins charg&eacute;es en code et ceci fera le bonheur des &ldquo;themers&rdquo;. C'est une am&eacute;lioration globale du syst&egrave;me et un pas en avant vers l'utilisation de technologies non "drupalienne". </span></span></p>
            <p><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></p> 
